:hidden dark:bg-[#484848]/30">MistralAIDetectorForSequenceClassification</c=
ode> class, which serves as the foundational architecture for both classifi=
cation and detection tasks in GigaCheck. This class wraps the Mistral-7B-v0=
.3 transformer model and extends it with task-specific components: a classi=
fication head for document-level predictions and optional DETR components f=
or character-level interval detection.</p>
<p>For details on the classification head and LoRA configuration, see <a hr=
ef=3D"https://deepwiki.com/ai-forever/gigacheck/5.2-classification-head-and=
-lora" class=3D"text-neutral-300 hover:text-neutral-200 hover:underline">Cl=
assification Head and LoRA</a>. For the DETR detection architecture, see <a=
 href=3D"https://deepwiki.com/ai-forever/gigacheck/5.3-detr-detection-archi=
tecture" class=3D"text-neutral-300 hover:text-neutral-200 hover:underline">=
DETR Detection Architecture</a>. For training procedures, see <a href=3D"ht=
tps://deepwiki.com/ai-forever/gigacheck/4.1-classification-model-training" =
class=3D"text-neutral-300 hover:text-neutral-200 hover:underline">Classific=
ation Model Training</a> and <a href=3D"https://deepwiki.com/ai-forever/gig=
acheck/4.2-detection-model-training" class=3D"text-neutral-300 hover:text-n=
eutral-200 hover:underline">Detection Model Training</a>.</p>
