48]/30">"mistralai/Mistral-7B-v0.3"</code>).</p>
<p>The backbone processes input tokens through its decoder layers and produ=
ces hidden states of shape <code class=3D"rounded-sm bg-[#e5e5e5] px-[0.25r=
em] py-[0.20rem] text-xs font-normal leading-[15px] before:hidden after:hid=
den dark:bg-[#484848]/30">(batch_size, sequence_length, hidden_size)</code>=
